Lecture 17: Regularization Networks  
Tomaso Poggio 

Description 
We describe Radial Basis Function networks and RBF extensions such as 
Hyper Basis Functions. We derive the relation with additive models, with 
various types of splines and with other types of neural network 
architectures.  

  
Suggested Reading 
•  Girosi, Jones and Poggio. Regularization Theory and Neural 
Networks Architectures Neural Computation, Vol 7, 219-269, 
1995.  
•  Hertz, Krogh, and Palmer. Introduction to the Theory of Neural 
Computation Addison Wesley, 1991.  

 

 

